 havelock europa in the last ten years our customers have taken us far and wide for over  years havelock europa has been a key player in the interiors market both in the uk and internationally we provide a flexible approach that encompasses design manufacture kitting logistics and installation of furniture our experienced interior upgrade and refurbishment contracting teams seamlessly dovetail into our overall offer allowing for true turnkey delivery of projects and rollout programmes operating in our chosen sectors are retail financial services education health corporate offices accommodation and leisure   we understand the sectorspecific challenges our customers face and by applying our experience we create appropriate innovative and affordable interior solutions a business built around our customers we put customers at the heart of our business and work handinhand with them to understand their needs together we deliver worldclass innovative solutions we thrive on helping our customers succeed  our continual focus on delivering to expectations on time and on budget in a sustainable way keeps our customers returning again and again we are proud to be working with some of the leading high street brands including walgreens alliance boots lloyds banking group marks  spencer primark  accessorize and house of fraser as well as a wide range of leading new space contractors including balfour beatty morgan sindall bam carillion wates and interserve led from the uk we have followed our customers into europe and asia where we are now investing and growing our capability to meet their overseas aspirations about us board of directorsgroup structurechronologysafety and sustainabilityour customers havelock europa plc  esa mcintosh  stage systems havelock europa plc search about us sectors services case studies news investor relations press careers contact us vision to be the world leader in interior fitout and refurbishment philosophy we put our customers first expertise world c